She's a 22 year-old sewist and designer based out of Tacoma, Washington. 🌲 @palomitaxo 

Her passion for fashion and all things sewing began when her mother showed her how to hand stitch using her grandma’s sewing kit. Since then, that passion grew and Paloma began designing beautiful garments of her own. 

Her collection is inspired by things that make you feel like the best version of yourself, featuring patchwork designs and  cutouts, in modern silhouettes. 🧵
